  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AudioController
    This class is the controller for the audio Allows the user to toggle the background music, or increase/decrease the sound
    AudioPlayer
    This class is used to manage the game music and other audio
    Bank
    The Bank_class is used to do transactions between players
    BankTest  
    BoardController<stage>
    This class is the controller for the main board view, which is also the main view for the game itself.
    Building
    This class is used to create a building
    BuildingTest  
    BuyPropertyController
    This class is the controller for the 'Buy Property'-view It handles all UI-interaction when buying a property
    Card
    The Card_class is used to create a card Card has description,transaction value,position
    CardTest  
    CheckInboxController
    This class is the controller for the check-inbox view It displays information about the user having to check their email
    ConnectionPool
    This class sets up a connection pool
    ControllerMediator  
    ControllerMediator.ControllerMediatorHolder  
    CustomTheme
    This class creates a new custom theme
    Database
    The Database-class is the class that does all the direct communication between the java-application and the database.
    DatabaseListener
    The DatabaseListener-class is used to keep track when certain values of interest changes in the database
    DatabaseManager
    The DatabaseManager-class is used to manage the communication with the database
    Dice
    The Dice_class used to return a random value every time Throw Dice button clicked in the game
    Email
    The Email-class is used to handle everything that has to do with emails
    FeedbackController
    This class is the controller of the feedback view.
    FieldInitializer
    This class is used to initialize the different fields on the board
    ForgotPasswordController
    This class is the controller for the forgotPassword view
    Game
    This class is used for communication between game logic, database and UI
    Hotel
    This class is used to create a hotel
    House
    This class is used for creating houses
    IMediateControllers
    This class is an interface allowing communication between different controllers
    InfoDialogController
    This class is the controller for the Alertbox dialog
    LocalStorage
    This class is used for storing user data locally (.txt file)
    LoginController
    This class is the controller for the login view
    MyPropertiesController
    This class is the controller for the MyProperties dialog
    OptionsController
    This class is the controller of the options view It handles all the UI-interaction concerning the settings
    Password
    This class is used for managing a password
    Player
    The Player_class is used to do everything has to do with player such username,position,balance,nickname...
    PlayerTest  
    PreloaderController
    This class is a preloader that initializes the board by communicating with the database and setting some variables
    Property
    The Property class is used to manage properties
    PropertyController
    This class is the controller for the property dialog
    PropertyTest  
    Quiz
    The Quiz-class is used to create quizzes.
    QuizController  
    QuizInitializer
    This class is used to initialize a list of quizzes
    QuizTest  
    RegisterController
    This class registers a user
    RegisteredController
    This class shows a window that says the user successfully got registered
    Runner
    This class is used to run the application/game, and displays the main window.
    SettingsController
    This class is the controller for the settings view It handles all the UI-interaction concerning the settings
    Street
    The Street_class is used to create street Street has name, and contains array of properties
    StreetTest  
    ThemeController
    This class is the controller of the theme view It handles all the UI-interaction concerning the themes
    ThemeEditorController
    This view lets the user make a custom theme Note: Because stylesheets are cached in JavaFX, the application needs to be restarted before the custom theme can be applied
    Upgrade
    The Upgrade_class is used to create Upgrade..
    UpgradeTest  
    wildCardController
    This class is the controller of the wildcard view
    Window
    This class is used to initialize and set up the main window for the game
    WindowManager
    This class is used to handle all scene and stage changes
